abstract: Venus Williams defeats Belinda Bencic of Switzerland, 6-1, 6-2, in first round of Dubai Tennis Championships.
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams, the defending champion, beat an opponent half her age, Belinda Bencic, 17, of Switzerland, in the first round of the Dubai Tennis Championships.
